ProfessionL,is,a,recruitment,management,platform,It,allows,employers,to,manage,their,recruitment,searches,from,a,single,dashboard,The,dashboard,includes,tabs,for,several,aspects,of,recruitment,including,multiple,job,listings,candidates,and,contacts,An,Activity,tab,allows,an,overall,view,of,the,recruitment,process,workflow,The,ProfessionL,API,exposes,the,user,profile,functionality,and,enables,data,portability,for,importation,and,exportation